| Plot                    = Welcome to Avengers HQ, the state-of-the-art facility where Earth's mightiest heroes assemble to monitor and protect the galaxy. This ultra high-tech building is surrounded by F.R.I.D.A.Y., an A.I. that helps the Avengers identify threats and support the entire Campus. Once inside, recruits encounter Iron Man who presents his latest hypersonic intervention. Suddenly, F.R.I.D.A.Y. sounds a yellow alert... Kree Missiles detected! Their target: Planet Earth! Board one of the hypersonic vehicles and blast off into space to divert the missiles so Iron Man and Captain Marvel can avert the danger. Good luck recruits... Earth is counting on you!
