| Notes                  = * When [[Anthony Stark (Earth-TRN971)|Iron Man]] contacts Rocket for support during the pre-show, [[89P13 (Earth-TRN971)|Rocket]] states "Look, we need a hand! Like an actual hand!" which is a reference to the plot of {{ml|Guardians of the Galaxy - Mission: BREAKOUT!}} where Rocket requires the hands of the [[Humans (Homo sapiens)|terran]] guests to free the [[Guardians of the Galaxy (Earth-TRN971)|Guardians of the Galaxy]].
| Trivia                 = * On September 2, 2019 ''Rock 'n' Roller Coaster'' was closed for an extensive refurbishment and retheming to become ''Avengers Assemble: Flight Force''.
* While trying to contact reinforcements, [[F.R.I.D.A.Y. (Earth-TRN971)|F.R.I.D.A.Y.]] contacts several characters associated with other attractions including:
** [[89P13 (Earth-TRN971)|Rocket]] while he is trying to free the other [[Guardians of the Galaxy (Earth-TRN971)|Guardians of the Galaxy]] in {{ml|Guardians of the Galaxy - Mission: BREAKOUT!}}.
** [[Scott Lang (Earth-TRN971)|Ant-Man]] during a battle in {{ml|Ant-Man and the Wasp: Nano Battle!}}
** [[Samuel Wilson (Earth-TRN971)|Captain America]] and [[Kamala Khan (Earth-TRN971)|Ms. Marvel]] on-board the [[Disney Wish|The Disney Wish Cruise Liner]], home to the [[Worlds of Marvel]], during [[Avengers: Quantum Encounter]].
